title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Apr 27 2022
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Apr 27 2022
description:
Democrats Want Illegal Aliens Flooding The Country - Sen. Joe Manchin says not to end Title 42. Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene talks about the lawsuit to keep her off the ballot in Georgia. Sen. Rick Scott talked about his recent trip to Europe- and the Biden mishandling of the crisis at the US southern border. Pennsylvania Senate Candidate Dave McCormick talks about the state of the race.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
